by an immortal-binding formation.

00:36:19.920 --> 00:36:21.580
The Kunlun Mirror was stolen,

00:36:21.900 --> 00:36:23.760
and the man never appeared again.

00:36:25.320 --> 00:36:26.110
It turned out

00:36:28.370 --> 00:36:30.910
the strange disease was just a trap.

00:36:32.280 --> 00:36:34.190
The purpose was to make
Immortal Lord work tirelessly

00:36:34.190 --> 00:36:35.190
to assemble the Kunlun Mirror,

00:36:35.190 --> 00:36:37.280
so they could the mirror
to gain favor with the human emperor

00:36:37.280 --> 00:36:40.140
to become the imperial son-in-law
and gain wealth.

00:36:40.670 --> 00:36:44.330
Immortal Lord's powers were dispersed
by the binding formation.

00:36:46.440 --> 00:36:47.550
In desperation,

00:36:50.000 --> 00:36:52.300
she recited the Heart-Burning Incantation,

00:36:52.300 --> 00:36:54.160
transforming her original heart

00:36:56.920 --> 00:36:59.000
into a crystal heart.

00:36:59.360 --> 00:37:01.490
She abandoned her immortal identity—

00:37:01.630 --> 00:37:03.090
changing from an immortal

00:37:03.960 --> 00:37:05.200
into a spirit.

00:37:06.010 --> 00:37:09.270
The immortal-binding formation
could no longer trap her.

00:37:10.940 --> 00:37:12.800
She broke through the formation,

00:37:13.320 --> 00:37:15.070
and ripped out the hearts...

00:37:18.100 --> 00:37:20.080
of that man's entire family.

00:37:27.110 --> 00:37:27.920
From then on,

00:37:31.030 --> 00:37:33.560
there was no place for her
in the Three Realms.

00:37:34.030 --> 00:37:36.290
She had to find this otherworldly island

00:37:36.300 --> 00:37:37.810
beyond the Three Realms

00:37:38.400 --> 00:37:40.130
and outside the five elements.

00:37:40.320 --> 00:37:41.250
But spirits

00:37:41.480 --> 00:37:43.630
need large amounts of human essence

00:37:44.000 --> 00:37:46.630
to maintain their demonic powers
and appearance.

00:37:46.630 --> 00:37:47.960
For thousands of years,

00:37:49.760 --> 00:37:50.880
